ğŸ“œ Download extracted text.

ğŸ“Š Extract tables (structured & unstructured formats).

âœ… Download extracted tables as Excel files.

ğŸ“¦ Dependencies

Before running the project, ensure you have the following Python packages installed:

pip install streamlit pandas openpyxl requests

ğŸ› ï¸ Setup and Running the App

Clone or Download this repository.

Install dependencies (if not already installed):

pip install -r requirements.txt

Run the Streamlit app:

streamlit run app.py

ğŸ”‘ Configuration

Update the API Key in app.py before running the script:

client = LLMWhispererClientV2(
    base_url="https://llmwhisperer-api.us-central.unstract.com/api/v2",
    api_key="YOUR_API_KEY_HERE"  # Replace with your actual API key
)

